            "description": "Indexes are not unique. (errorCode 1)\nSome input types are invalid. (errorCode 2)\nSome return types are invalid. (errorCode 3)\n ReturnType,Index or VaultId is missing. (errorcode 3)\nInvalid vault id length - length of vault id is 32. (errorcode 5)\nSome vault ids are invalid. Only alphanumerics are allowed. (errorcode 9)",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorEntity"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "500": {
            "description": "Internal server error. (errorCode 0)",
            "content": {
